77             ===============================================================
78             FILE PROVIDER — required for sharing PDF Skill Passports
79             ===============================================================
80             FileProvider converts a raw File path into a content:// URI
81             that other apps (PDF viewers, email clients, Drive) can open
82             without needing direct filesystem permissions.
83
84             HOW IT WORKS:
85               1. SkillPassportGenerator writes the PDF to
86                  getExternalFilesDir("passports")
87               2. VaultScreenEnhanced calls FileProvider.getUriForFile()
88                  to get a content:// URI for that file
89               3. An Intent with ACTION_VIEW + FLAG_GRANT_READ_URI_PERMISSION
90                  opens the PDF in any installed viewer
91
92             AUTHORITY RULE:
93               The authority string MUST be "${applicationId}.fileprovider"
94               exactly. It is referenced in VaultScreenEnhanced as:
95               "${context.packageName}.fileprovider"
96               Both must match or the URI will fail to resolve.
97
98             PATH CONFIG:
99               android:resource="@xml/file_paths" points to
